712432f-a.title: Manhattan: 37th Street - 9th Avenue
712432f-a.text:
37th Street, south side, west from but not including Ninth Avenue.
The house at the left is No. 402 West 37th Street.
August 30, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

712434f-a.title: Manhattan: 37th Street (West) - 9th Avenue
712434f-a.text:
432-456 West 37th Street, south side, west from a point midway between
Ninth and Tenth Aves and to the latter. No. 432 is fairly new, replacing
two three-story frame houses. No. 434-436 is the New York County Jail,
formerly the 22nd Precinct Police Station. The 12-story Underhill
Building covers house numbers 438-448.
May 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
